Okay <@U286Q175Y>, feedback so far:

• When you import a deck, it seems like the card editions are sorted at random. While it is nice to see all the pretty foil time-stamps I could fill a deck with, why not have them automatically inserted with the cheapest version of the card?
• A "Next Turn" button in the playtester would be nice.
• When goldfishing, I also want to know what turn it is, so a turn counter in the playtester would be good as well.
• In the Deck Stats piechart, Artifact Creatures show up as both Artifacts and Creatures.
• An option to sort the *entire* deck by CMC would be nice, rather than it sorting by CMC within each type.
Obviously, some of that is fairly nitpicky, but you did ask.
The import thing is a pretty big annoyance, though.
